snippet.title: Two Point Hospital: Off The Grid | Announce Trailer
snippet.description:
Make Two Point County green again... for the very first time, with our new DLC Two Point Hospital: Off the Grid! 

Two Point Hospital: Off the Grid is available now for pre-purchase with an early adopters discount of 10%, and launches on 18th March 2020 on PC.

Join Two Point County's ever-present Mayor, Tabitha Windsock as she campaigns for re-election using eco-friendly means as her main goal. You'll face new challenges from gameplay mechanics, illnesses and more in three brand new locations!
